    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! It has been such a reliable and fun ride for me, and I'm honestly going to miss it. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It runs beautifully and looks great, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for something dependable and high-quality without the brand-new price tag. I'd love to see it go to a great home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 29900.0,
