    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers peak torque through a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains taut with refreshed subframe bushings. Rod bearing service has been proactively addressed, and the throttle actuators are recently indexed. While the Alpine White finish shows minor road-rash and the interior exhibits typical bolster wear, the powertrain integrity and 8,400 RPM redline performance are uncompromising. A purist\u2019s spec for those prioritizing drivetrain excellence over concours aesthetics.",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
