    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 996.2-generation Carrera, powered by the 3.6L flat-six engine featuring Variocam Plus valve timing. This unit delivers a broad torque curve through a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing its original multi-link rear setup and McPherson struts for precise turn-in and high-speed stability. The hydraulic steering rack provides excellent feedback, and the four-piston monobloc calipers offer firm, fade-resistant deceleration. While displaying minor aesthetic patina indicative of its 'good' condition, the drivetrain is thermally stable and free of bore scoring symptoms. A high-performance driver\u2019s car optimized for the purist.",
